---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Workers Compensation Insurance — Pink Payroll" description="Pay-as-you-go workers comp insurance integrated with your payroll. No large deposits, no audits, and accurate premiums — powered by Pink Payroll in California.">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-[#F3BD33]/10 border-b border-[#F3BD33]/30">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 text-center">
      <p class="text-[#F3BD33] text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Workers Compensation Insurance</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-brand-black mb-6 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Stop Overpaying for Workers' Comp: Pay-As-You-Go is Here.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-brand-gray text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10">
        Pink Payroll connects your payroll directly to your insurance policy. No big deposits. No audit surprises. Just accurate, automatic coverage.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/contact" class="bg-pink text-white font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-pink-dark transition-colors text-base">
          Request a Workers' Comp Quote
        </a>
        <a href="https://link.pinkpayroll.com/widget/booking/gZIYVYUm3txLBKTRjTZd" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="bg-white border-2 border-brand-black text-brand-black font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors text-base">
          Schedule a Payroll Consultation
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Pay-As-You-Go -->
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-brand-black mb-4">Why Pay-As-You-Go?</h2>
    <p class="text-brand-gray text-lg mb-4 max-w-3xl">
      Traditional workers' comp is a guessing game. You estimate your payroll, pay a massive deposit, and pray you don't get hit with a huge bill at the end of the year.
    </p>
    <p class="text-brand-black font-bold text-lg mb-12">The Pink Way is different.</p>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">

      <div class="bg-white border border-brand-light-gray rounded-2xl p-8">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[#F3BD33]/20 text-[#F3BD33] font-extrabold flex items-center justify-center text-lg mb-5">1</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-black mb-3">No Large Upfront Deposits</h3>
        <p class="text-brand-gray text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Stop tying up your cash. With Pay-As-You-Go, your premium is paid in small increments as payroll occurs. Improve your cash flow starting Day 1.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border border-brand-light-gray rounded-2xl p-8">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[#F3BD33]/20 text-[#F3BD33] font-extrabold flex items-center justify-center text-lg mb-5">2</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-black mb-3">Premiums Based on Reality, Not Estimates</h3>
        <p class="text-brand-gray text-sm leading-relaxed">
          We calculate your premium using real-time payroll numbers from every pay period. Your policy stays 100% accurate, 100% of the time.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border border-brand-light-gray rounded-2xl p-8">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[#F3BD33]/20 text-[#F3BD33] font-extrabold flex items-center justify-center text-lg mb-5">3</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-black mb-3">"Audit Headaches" Minimized</h3>
        <p class="text-brand-gray text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Audits are a fact of life, but they don't have to be a nightmare. Because Pink Payroll organizes your reporting automatically, we provide the documentation auditors need so you can get back to work.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How It Works -->
  <section class="bg-brand-light-gray/40 border-y border-brand-light-gray">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-brand-black mb-12 text-center">How the Automatic Sync Works</h2>
      <ol class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        {[
          { step: '1', title: 'Payroll is Processed', desc: 'You run payroll through Pink Payroll as usual.' },
          { step: '2', title: 'Secure Reporting', desc: 'Totals are sent automatically to your carrier.' },
          { step: '3', title: 'Calculated Accuracy', desc: 'Premiums are based on actual wages paid.' },
          { step: '4', title: 'Automatic Payment', desc: 'The correct amount is paid. No checks to write.' },
        ].map(({ step, title, desc }) => (
          <li class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-brand-light-gray p-6 text-center">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[#F3BD33] text-white font-extrabold flex items-center justify-center text-lg mx-auto mb-4">{step}</div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-black mb-2">{title}</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-gray text-sm leading-relaxed">{desc}</p>
          </li>
        ))}
      </ol>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Get a Quote CTA -->
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
    <div class="bg-[#F3BD33]/10 border border-[#F3BD33]/40 rounded-3xl p-10 md:p-14">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-brand-black mb-4">Need a Quote? Get One in 24 Hours.</h2>
      <p class="text-brand-gray text-lg mb-6 max-w-2xl">
        Through our sister company, <strong class="text-brand-black">Benefits Wheel Insurance</strong>, we offer a "Total Protection" package.
      </p>
      <ul class="space-y-3 mb-10">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-brand-gray">
          <span class="text-[#F3BD33] font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
          <span><strong class="text-brand-black">Fast Turnaround:</strong> Quotes usually delivered within 24 hours.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-brand-gray">
          <span class="text-[#F3BD33] font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
          <span><strong class="text-brand-black">Expert Guidance:</strong> We ensure you are using the correct class codes (so you don't overpay).</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-brand-gray">
          <span class="text-[#F3BD33] font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
          <span><strong class="text-brand-black">Major Carriers:</strong> We work with AmTrust, The Hartford, Travelers, and more.</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-pink text-white font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-pink-dark transition-colors text-base">
        Request a Workers' Comp Quote
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Industries -->
  <section class="bg-brand-black text-white">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold mb-4">Solutions for Every Industry</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        From the high-risk demands of <strong class="text-white">Construction</strong> and <strong class="text-white">Manufacturing</strong> to the specific needs of <strong class="text-white">Restaurants, Attorneys, and Retail</strong>, we understand your industry's specific compliance requirements.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Pink Payroll -->
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-brand-black mb-10 text-center">Why California Businesses Choose Pink Payroll</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">

      <div class="text-center px-4">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-pink/10 text-pink flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-black mb-2">Seamless Integration</h3>
        <p class="text-brand-gray text-sm">Payroll and Insurance in one dashboard.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center px-4">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-pink/10 text-pink flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-black mb-2">Cash Flow First</h3>
        <p class="text-brand-gray text-sm">Keep your money in your business longer.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center px-4">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-pink/10 text-pink flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.948V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 8V5z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-black mb-2">Local Support</h3>
        <p class="text-brand-gray text-sm">A team that actually answers the phone when you have a question.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Final CTA -->
  <section class="bg-pink text-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold mb-4">Protect Your Business Today</h2>
      <p class="text-pink-light text-lg mb-10">Don't wait for your next audit to wish you had switched.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/contact" class="bg-white text-pink font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors text-base">
          Request a Workers' Comp Quote
        </a>
        <a href="https://link.pinkpayroll.com/widget/booking/gZIYVYUm3txLBKTRjTZd" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="border-2 border-white text-white font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors text-base">
          Schedule a Payroll Consultation
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
